summary:
This took too long to make, it's 4x longer than Bullet Bill 1 and it uses mouse control (which a lot of you asked for). It also has checkpoints, multiple levels (i.e. Castle, Underground) and boss fights! Hopefully you have a decent computer so it won't lag. ^^;

If you come across any glitches in the game. please PM me so I can get it sorted.

Have fun!

In this bundle we present you our two puzzle games for you relaxing and collecting all achievements while you playing single or with your friends!

IIN - You are a soul who controls cubes, overcoming challenges to open and enter the portals, your true goal;

Goroons - it's a game about cooperation, communication, and cute monsters with unique abilities!"
